        <item>
            <title>0.3.499</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2026 08:41:13 -0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>499</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.3.499</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>ChainLink 0.3.499</h2>
<p class="sub">Coach Insights numbers now match the calendar.</p>

<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Coach Insights no longer double-counts rides that arrive from two
  connected services (e.g. Garmin <em>and</em> Strava). Training-load
  warnings, the Monday weekly review and record detection now use the same
  numbers as the training calendar — no more "1088 TSS" cards for a
  558-TSS week.</li>
  <li>Load warnings are now honest about their window: they look at your
  <b>last 7 days</b> (rolling), not the calendar week.</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
